# Mario Kart ML Tutor

This project is a machine learning tutor focused on Mario Kart gameplay. It aims to help users understand and apply machine learning techniques using data and scenarios inspired by Mario Kart.

## Features

- Tutorials on basic and advanced machine learning concepts
- Example datasets based on Mario Kart 8 kaggle dataset : https://www.kaggle.com/datasets/marlowspringmeier/mario-kart-8-deluxe-ingame-statistics
- Code samples for data analysis and model training
- Testing the results and predition in a streamlit interactive app
- Interactive questions and challenges

## Getting Started

1. Clone the repository:
   ```
   git clone https://github.com/yourusername/Mario-kart-ML-tutor.git
   ```
2. Install dependencies:
   ```
   pip install -r requirements.txt
   ```
3. Run the tutorials or scripts as described in the documentation.

## Folder Structure

- `data/` - Sample datasets
- Jupyter notebooks with tutorials
- `app/` - model and streamlit app
- `readMe` - Project documentation
- `rapports` - Project notebooks execution
- `figures` - figures generated from the notebooks
- `images` - app images
